# Dev Workflow

## Git

- Branches: `feature/<topic>`, `fix/<topic>`, `refactor/<topic>` — never commit to `main`
- Commits: imperative mood (e.g. "Add reward shaping for distance")
- Verify current branch before committing (PR merges may leave you on `main`)
- If pre-commit hooks reject, fix and new commit (no `--amend`/`--no-verify`)
- After pushing a feature branch, create PR via `gh pr create`

## Validation & Deps

- `just validate` (format + lint + test) before pushing
- Quick iteration: `just format && just lint`
- `uv add [--dev] <pkg>` for deps; `just dev-sync` after pulling lock changes; never edit `uv.lock`

## Training

- `just train <config.yaml> [mlp|transformer]` (defaults to transformer)
- Configs in `examples/env_config/`; logs to Wandb; checkpoints in `checkpoints/`
- CLI: `--record-during-training`, `--max-epochs`, `--render-mode`
- Hyperparams in `DQNConfig`/`TrainingConfig` (`model/dqn/config.py`) — change there, not CLI
- `just profile <config> [model] [epochs]` · `just simulate-latest [mlp|transformer]` · `just clean`
